page.title: 01SELATTYN TODAY
page.content: {Selattyn is a very peaceful place.There is not very much traffic around. And there is very little rubbish around. The church is very old and it has got red tiles on the roof and is made of stone.Mr Jones shop is very old fashioned.Most of the houses are made of stone and have slates on the roof.There is lots of wildlife around the village.The church is in good condition.The school is sort of hidden by the trees and bushes. The village is very small.The new rectory is made of bricks and has got red tiles on the roof top. Most of the people go to work.The school is made of stones and has got red tiles on the roof.The roads are quite bendy There are some horse stables in the village they are made of bricks and some of the older stables are made out of stone .The only entertainment is
